==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scot-free
<hw>Scot"-free"</hw> <pr><mark>[?]</mark></pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free
from payment of scot; untaxed; hence, unhurt; clear; safe.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Do as much for this purpose, and thou shalt pass
<qex>scot-free</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Then young Hay escaped <qex>scot-free</qex> to Holland.</q>
<rj><qau>A. Lang.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scoth</ent>⟦br⟧
